{
  "id": "RAW_027f34db",
  "title": "深度｜中国具身智能突围，核心靠“体”更靠“脑”",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI4NTgxMDk1NA==&mid=2247513294&idx=1&sn=3efae3c6d0de59b882fcce977dcdb20a",
  "date": "2026-01-08 02:03:00",
  "author": "Z Potentials",
  "siteName": "Z Potentials",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><font face=\"黑体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">当宇树机器人跳秧歌、智元人形机亮相发布会的视频刷屏社交平台，当各类人形机器人成为科技圈</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">“流量明星”，具身智能赛道正迎来热度高峰。</span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">这场技术狂欢背后，</span></span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">需要</span></span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">“体” 与 “脑” 的协同进化。</span>“体” 作为机器人物理载体，是应用落地的基础——没有精密机械臂、灵活移动底盘，再先进的 “脑” 也无法将决策转化为动作。可在硬件制造能力日益趋同的今天，“体”的优势难以成为绝对壁垒，决定产业突围高度的核心变量，正在转向 “脑” 的竞争力。具身智能大模型的强弱，直接关系到中国能否在这一赛道领跑全球。</span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">此前，衡量</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">“脑”的强弱缺乏统一标准，行业深陷“Demo炫技”“自说自话”的困境，仿真测试与现实脱节制约发展。</span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">2025 年 10 月，Dexmal 原力灵机联合 Hugging Face 推出 RoboChallenge。作为全球首个大规模多任务真机基准测试平台，它相当于为具身模型搭建了 “全球统考考场”，让 “脑” 的实力有了量化标尺。</span>这一平台整合全球主流机型，配备高清传感设备，测试集含30个日常任务（远超行业常规3-5个），通过“视觉输入匹配”保障测试公平，更以云端远程服务降低验证成本，倒逼行业从“炫技”转向“实干”。</span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.40370370370370373\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100029639\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=654a7ae7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FZ300vPwLQklu0Gkb5CibwIvOHQ98wqasTsGR2DWck2CKEQLoiaPqQn72CQ4yN4wIK99p5L2b08dyEqJ4W2F5no5Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:center;margin-right:16px;\"><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-size: 12px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk4388vztvq\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mk4388x3105b\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;outline: 0px;font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align: center;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 2;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;visibility: visible;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-style: italic;\">图片来源：RoboChallenge</span></span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">就在这个全球顶尖</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">“考场” 上，中国企业交出亮眼答卷：自变量机器人</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">开源的</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">自研</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">具身模型</span></font><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">&nbsp;WALL-OSS，以 46.43 分超越美国 PI 公司的 π</span><font face=\"Cambria Math\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">₀</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">模型，拿下全球开源模型总分第二，更在叠洗碗巾、挂口杯、按按钮等</span></font><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">&nbsp;6 个单任务中排名第一。</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">WALL-OSS 的突围，足以证明中国在具身智能 “大脑” 领域的</span></span><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">实力</span></span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">进步</span></span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">——当开源的自研模型跻身全球第一梯队的行列，中国</span></span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">就有了在这条赛道上跑出一个</span></span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">“本土版Open AI”的可能</span></span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">。</span></span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5675925925925925\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100029635\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f24c23a4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FZ300vPwLQklu0Gkb5CibwIvOHQ98wqasTibSPWFZgADOo0picfiaHUwONARic03CDxzIzB45VmjB74GDxsibTKmRXH1w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:center;margin-right:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-size: 12px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk4388vztvq\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mk4388x3105b\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-style: italic;\">图片来源：RoboChallenge</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">WALL-OSS</span></span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">的</span></span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">开源是彻底的，它不是简单地提供一个模型，而是公开了一整套</span></span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">可复现的方案，包括预训练模型权重、训练代码、数据集接口，以及详细部署文档等。</span></span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">这样的</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">“真开源”，让开发者无需从零开始搭建框架，仅凭RTX4090级显卡，</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">就能完成全流程开发，外部团队一周即可实现和机器人的适配</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">，</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">社区开发者使用模型的便利性得到大幅提升。</span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">WALL-OSS的彻底开源，也意味着它在具身智能测试中的表现，</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">更能经得起</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">最严苛</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">的检验。具身智能模型测试，不同于大模型测试，它的测评要提前公开任务，类似于开卷考试，最终看的是视频</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">动作</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">。在这种情况下，只有</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">完全公开代码的开源模型，才意味着它</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">并没有通过微调模型来</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">“冲榜”，而</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">是真正货真价实、具有应变能力的</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">“真大脑”。</span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">从产业规律看，凭借着强大的制造业实力，中国已在</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">“体”的硬件端形成全球优势，宇树、智元、优必选等企业的机器人本体技术日趋成熟，长三角、珠三角产业链供应链配套完备。但过去，</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">由于</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">缺乏强大自主</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">的</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">“大脑”，“体” 的潜力往往难以得到有效释放，</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">行业</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">甚至陷入</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">“硬件先进、功能落后” 的尴尬境地。</span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">WALL-OSS 的开源，正好补上这一短板，</span></span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">不仅</span></span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">形成</span></span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">“脑体协同效应”</span></span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">，更能够形成一个健康</span></span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">可持续的行业生态</span></span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">。</span></span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">一方面，现有的硬件公司</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">可以将自身的硬件产品和开源底座快速适配，进一步推动本体性能的优化和场景落地。另一方面，</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">原来没有能力做基础模型的一些中小开发者，比如一般高校或者小型企业，也可以使用基础开源模型，去做具身智能方面的</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">垂直</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">应用，丰富整个行业的生态。</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">这种</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">“技术突破+场景赋能”的模式，</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">曾经有力助推中国新能源、</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">5G等产业的发展，</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">也将带动中国具身智能行业的持续升级。</span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">更令人振奋的是，</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">“重视核心技术自主、强化脑体协同” 正成为国家层面共识。2026 年新年伊始，李强总理在深圳调研时，考察了优必选、云鲸和自变量三家具身智能企业。在考察自变量时，他观看了通用机器人 “量子 1 号” 基于WALL-OSS模型制作香囊的复杂任务，并对其技术探索给予了肯定。</span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">开年的</span></span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">调研释放清晰信号：在高质量发展背景下，具身智能作为新质生产力重要组成，需要</span></span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">“体脑兼备”。</span></span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">“体” 的硬件优势筑牢基础，“脑” 的自主突破拉升上限，再加上国家政策</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">层面</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">对科技创新的持续支持，</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">“脑体协同、生态共建、场景驱动” 的道路已然成型。</span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">未来，随着更多中国模型在全球舞台崭露头角，</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">“脑” 的赋能效应</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">将</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">持续凸显</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">。</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">中国具身智能</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">行业</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">不仅能产出更多</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">适配多元场景的</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">机器人，更能培育支撑千行百业的智能生态，在全球新一轮科技革命和产业变革中抢占先机，实现从</span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">“跟跑” 到 “领跑” 的全面突围。</span></font></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
